DESC:
The Oklahoma Air National Guard - Oklahoma City, OK is seeking the services for Gym Equipment Relocation.&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;
<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Scope: The contractor shall provide all personnel, equipment, tools, materials, supervision, and quality control necessary,<span style="COLOR: black"> except as specified in Paragraph 3.0 as Government Furnished, to perform</span> moving all 46 pieces of gym equipment, free weights, and dumbbells from the current building to building 1020.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Additionally, the contractor shall move all current gym equipment in 1020, to include the Rogue Monkey Rig, free weights, rowers, treadmill, stationary bike, rowers, ski ergo, free weights, dumbbells, bars, squat racks, gym accessories, pull-up bars, boxes, tires, gym flooring, and weight racks from building 1020 to building 1033.</span></p>
<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Background: The gym equipment, free weights, and flooring are currently all located at Will Rogers Guard base in building 1001.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>The gym equipment and flooring currently in 1020 will be moved to building 1033.<br /><br />Period of Performance: Shall be 4 days. <br /></span></p>
